Thomas A. Donovan wey be 37 years before, before Vice Presido, West Coast operation for dis hazardous waste site remediation, na im dem dey call executive vice president, and chief operating officer both newly created post, and one director filling vacancy.

Kanonie talk sey e dey anticipate sey im go name Oga Donovan to succeed Richard F. Brissette, 55, as Presido and Chief Executive Officer, effective March 1.

Mr. Brissette go remain on top Canonie board and e go be consultant to di company.

